      <odd id="aspace_8c102b1b8643ed1f859f951bd67c9814">
         <head>General note</head>
         <p>Forms part of Yale Record Group 7-A (YRG 7-A), Records of Yale officers and offices responsible for development policy and administration.</p>  
      </odd>
      <acqinfo id="aspace_63cf0e545166822b22b8fcb80971c92a">
         <head>Immediate Source of Acquisition</head>
         <p>Transferred from the Office of Development, 1997.</p>  
      </acqinfo>
      <accessrestrict id="aspace_02e40882632bed1e424ad89594cc9e2d">
         <head>Conditions Governing Access</head>
         <p>The materials are open for research.</p>
         <p>Original motion picture films and videotapes may not be played. Researchers must consult with reference archivist for policies and procedures governing the creation of duplicating master and use copies of original items.</p>  
      </accessrestrict>
      <prefercite id="aspace_6a8cd44caa5da437569c209e375f0012">
